      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-md shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-4">Track Your Expenses</h2>
          <p>Keep a record of every penny you spend. This will help you understand where your money is going and identify areas to cut back.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-md shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-4">Set Realistic Goals</h2>
          <p>Don't try to save too much too quickly. Set achievable goals and gradually increase your savings over time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-md shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-4">Use the 50/30/20 Rule</h2>
          <p>Allocate 50% of your income to needs, 30% to wants, and 20% to savings and debt repayment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-md shadow">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-4">Automate Your Savings</h2>
          <p>Set up automatic transfers to your savings account so you don't have to think about it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
